{"tid":700333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推倒樓市]政府擬一刀切對所有空置一段時期一手樓單位徵稅","createTime":"2018-06-13T09:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T09:58:27.000Z","uid":134683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4042e1ac98f6c0e157da952a54ced92ec84fae6","tid":700333,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"各位上車有望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n消息：政府擬一刀切對所有空置一段時期一手樓單位徵稅<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，有關空置稅的研究已到最後階段，本月內會交代，之後留待立法會辯論。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，政府研究的空置稅措施，只針對一手樓，不會涵蓋二手樓，亦預料會以一刀切方式，對空置了一段時間的大中小型一手樓單位徵稅。至於是否透過差餉等方式徵收，則暫時未有定案，仍然有待商討。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥將於明日凌晨出訪歐洲，本月26日早上返港。據了解，有關推行空置稅的措施，會待她回港後才公布。"},{"pid":"9e26530bf072562cbe070321a26788f67e43fba2","tid":700333,"uid":171901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"繼續升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2466ff159677e99c2170ebd17c273bb1500c065","tid":700333,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"一個新樓盤 所以900個單位一齊開賣<br />\n<br />\n今個月其中200有折扣優惠<br />\n<br />\n兩個月後另外200又有折扣優惠<br />\n<br />\n如此牙膏式折扣優惠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭可以點處理？"},{"pid":"7e6d865a429e86d5bb1004f2bd6fd4238ae5cb6e","tid":700333,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有用我裸跑又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa5592bb12fef6925e5dcceed98c9b12fb1fce5","tid":700333,"uid":137725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"又升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068dec